WEBVTT

00:01:35.780 --> 00:01:38.250
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.420 --> 00:01:41.300
[Episode 13]

00:01:41.780 --> 00:01:42.420
Yi Lan.

00:01:45.110 --> 00:01:45.970
Anything else?

00:01:50.590 --> 00:01:51.430
What's wrong?

00:01:51.990 --> 00:01:53.350
Spit it out.

00:01:57.300 --> 00:01:57.910
I like you.

00:02:04.300 --> 00:02:04.820
Me?

00:02:06.180 --> 00:02:07.960
Don't you have a girl you like?

00:02:09.550 --> 00:02:10.110
Yes.

00:02:11.470 --> 00:02:13.130
That girl has always been you.

00:02:18.020 --> 00:02:19.079
I reject you.

00:02:48.900 --> 00:02:50.460
The books are a bit messy.

00:03:09.870 --> 00:03:11.580
The speaker is covered in dust.

00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:13.620
It's been a few days since it was wiped.

00:03:13.620 --> 00:03:14.990
It needs to be wiped.

00:03:24.579 --> 00:03:25.870
Alright, alright.

00:03:26.579 --> 00:03:27.620
Stop wiping. Stop wiping.

00:03:27.620 --> 00:03:29.550
Move this cello to the repair room.

00:03:30.430 --> 00:03:32.030
Be careful, it's a bit heavy.

00:03:37.470 --> 00:03:38.060
Where are you going?

00:03:38.060 --> 00:03:39.590
The repair room is this way.

00:03:39.710 --> 00:03:40.300
Oh.

00:03:51.430 --> 00:03:51.990
Tell me.

00:03:54.500 --> 00:03:55.430
Tell you what?

00:03:56.020 --> 00:03:58.460
You're definitely hiding something
from me.

00:03:58.460 --> 00:03:59.460
Nothing.

00:04:01.430 --> 00:04:02.270
Tell me now.

00:04:03.580 --> 00:04:06.020
-It's hard to talk about.
-You have to! I give you 5 seconds!

00:04:06.020 --> 00:04:06.460
Five.

00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:06.780
Four.

00:04:06.780 --> 00:04:07.460
-I'll say it then!
-Three.

00:04:07.460 --> 00:04:07.740
Two.

00:04:07.740 --> 00:04:07.990
One.

00:04:07.990 --> 00:04:08.300
I'm going to say it.

00:04:08.300 --> 00:04:09.430
-Say it!
-I love you!

00:04:19.910 --> 00:04:21.029
Well...

00:04:21.470 --> 00:04:22.740
Shan,

00:04:23.030 --> 00:04:25.470
I think
I really have fallen in love with you.

00:04:25.470 --> 00:04:27.990
The kind of love a girl has for a boy.

00:04:28.660 --> 00:04:30.720
Do you know what Xiaoyi said love is?

00:04:31.060 --> 00:04:32.940
Love is when your face gets really hot.

00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:35.540
It turns red,
and your heart beats really fast.

00:04:35.620 --> 00:04:37.909
That day, it was raining and you
held the umbrella for me, remember?

00:04:37.909 --> 00:04:39.500
My face was very red,

00:04:39.500 --> 00:04:41.060
and my heart was beating really fast.

00:04:41.060 --> 00:04:42.030
And that's when I was sure.

00:04:42.030 --> 00:04:42.500
Wait a minute.

00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:42.909
I...

00:04:43.940 --> 00:04:45.540
I've fallen in love with you.

00:04:48.260 --> 00:04:49.060
Wait a minute.

00:04:50.940 --> 00:04:53.800
Where did you go
during these days you disappeared?

00:04:56.820 --> 00:04:59.220
I broke off my friendship
with Tong Xiaole.

00:05:03.500 --> 00:05:05.740
The person you've fallen in love with
definitely isn't me.

00:05:05.740 --> 00:05:07.650
The person I've fallen in love with
is you.

00:05:07.650 --> 00:05:09.010
Do you know what love is?

00:05:09.430 --> 00:05:10.060
Love is...

00:05:12.950 --> 00:05:13.410
Love...

00:05:24.770 --> 00:05:25.570
What's wrong?

00:05:25.700 --> 00:05:27.360
Is there something on my face?

00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:28.820
No.

00:05:29.350 --> 00:05:30.060
See?

00:05:30.180 --> 00:05:31.620
The person you love isn't me at all.

00:05:31.620 --> 00:05:33.110
What's between us is just

00:05:33.470 --> 00:05:34.740
a sibling-like bond.

00:05:36.590 --> 00:05:38.360
Besides, in my heart...

00:05:39.909 --> 00:05:42.440
there's always been someone
I can't let go of.

00:05:47.060 --> 00:05:47.940
Siblings?

00:05:53.260 --> 00:05:54.909
Then what is real love?

00:05:59.180 --> 00:06:00.430
What is love?

00:06:10.740 --> 00:06:11.620
Love is...

00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:17.880
It's that kind of...

00:06:18.380 --> 00:06:20.140
You want to be very close to him,

00:06:20.140 --> 00:06:22.380
but you can't be that close. That...

00:06:24.260 --> 00:06:25.460
That kind of feeling—

00:06:27.140 --> 00:06:27.940
it hurts.

00:06:32.909 --> 00:06:33.970
Do you understand?

00:07:09.470 --> 00:07:10.180
You are...

00:07:11.060 --> 00:07:11.600
Hello.

00:07:11.620 --> 00:07:12.820
My name is Luo Ningzi.

00:07:12.940 --> 00:07:14.470
I'm here for the interview.

00:07:17.820 --> 00:07:18.620
Luo Ningzi.

00:07:21.380 --> 00:07:22.380
Top of your major.

00:07:24.380 --> 00:07:25.060
Luo Ningzi,

00:07:25.820 --> 00:07:27.650
welcome to the Trio Orchestra.

00:07:29.700 --> 00:07:32.230
Don't I need to play on site
for the interview?

00:07:32.940 --> 00:07:34.940
Look. You're already top of your major.

00:07:34.940 --> 00:07:35.940
No need for an interview.

00:07:35.940 --> 00:07:37.490
Your cello skills must be very good.

00:07:37.490 --> 00:07:38.090
By the way,

00:07:38.380 --> 00:07:41.060
do you have time for a rehearsal
at 8 p.m. tomorrow?

00:07:41.060 --> 00:07:41.870
Yes.

00:07:42.820 --> 00:07:45.300
But I'd still like to ask

00:07:45.300 --> 00:07:46.380
about the performance fee.

00:07:46.380 --> 00:07:47.360
Don't worry.

00:07:47.740 --> 00:07:48.670
It's much higher

00:07:48.820 --> 00:07:50.420
than what you're expecting.

00:07:51.500 --> 00:07:53.250
Here. See you tomorrow.

00:07:53.590 --> 00:07:56.380
-Okay. I'll go back and prepare properly.
-Mm. Okay.

00:07:56.380 --> 00:07:56.980
Thank you.

00:07:57.620 --> 00:07:58.150
Go ahead.

00:08:05.260 --> 00:08:06.390
You can come out now.

00:08:11.700 --> 00:08:12.620
Yu.

00:08:15.140 --> 00:08:16.700
Luo Ningzi is very outstanding.

00:08:16.700 --> 00:08:17.620
Even without your recommendation,

00:08:17.620 --> 00:08:19.060
she could still get in.

00:08:19.820 --> 00:08:21.950
Top of her major at Hailan University.

00:08:23.060 --> 00:08:23.940
I heard you...

00:08:24.910 --> 00:08:25.990
like this watch very much.

00:08:25.990 --> 00:08:26.940
No need. No need.

00:08:27.820 --> 00:08:30.880
Just consider it me asking you
to take good care of Ning.

00:08:32.380 --> 00:08:32.950
What?

00:08:34.140 --> 00:08:35.470
Is she your girlfriend?

00:08:36.950 --> 00:08:38.500
You even noticed that?

00:08:38.590 --> 00:08:40.120
It's pretty obvious, okay?

00:08:41.380 --> 00:08:41.980
By the way,

00:08:42.380 --> 00:08:44.140
learning the cello is very expensive.
Right?

00:08:44.140 --> 00:08:46.940
Is it okay for her
to work and study at the same time?

00:08:49.380 --> 00:08:50.380
Ning's family...

00:08:50.500 --> 00:08:51.760
ran into some trouble.

00:08:52.140 --> 00:08:53.380
If she has any situation in the future,

00:08:53.380 --> 00:08:54.910
just let me know privately.

00:08:55.350 --> 00:08:56.500
But be sure to remember,

00:08:56.500 --> 00:08:59.020
don't bring this up in front of her.

00:08:59.380 --> 00:09:00.660
Don't worry.

00:09:02.150 --> 00:09:03.010
That's good.

00:09:39.420 --> 00:09:39.990
Sir.

00:09:40.230 --> 00:09:42.540
Thank you for coming to see me
despite your busy schedule.

00:09:42.540 --> 00:09:43.450
Mm. Not bad.

00:09:44.260 --> 00:09:45.260
Let me introduce her to you.

00:09:45.260 --> 00:09:46.660
This is our violist.

00:09:47.540 --> 00:09:48.470
You played well.

00:09:48.500 --> 00:09:49.280
Thank you.

00:09:50.020 --> 00:09:50.660
Cai Yu,

00:09:51.230 --> 00:09:52.500
your cellist

00:09:52.540 --> 00:09:53.940
performed very well too.

00:09:54.620 --> 00:09:56.500
Then... let me introduce her to you.

00:09:56.500 --> 00:09:56.900
Okay.

00:09:57.500 --> 00:09:58.260
You two chat.

00:09:58.420 --> 00:09:58.870
Okay.

00:10:00.500 --> 00:10:02.140
In this field,

00:10:02.500 --> 00:10:04.740
what expectations
do you have for yourself?

00:10:04.740 --> 00:10:06.350
I want to keep improving.

00:10:06.870 --> 00:10:07.230
Ning,

00:10:07.620 --> 00:10:09.780
my mentor specially came
to see my performance.

00:10:09.780 --> 00:10:11.540
The chief conductor
of the Dream Orchestra.

00:10:11.540 --> 00:10:13.000
You must have heard of him.

00:10:13.260 --> 00:10:15.570
Every music student probably knows him.

00:10:16.020 --> 00:10:16.620
Besides,

00:10:17.260 --> 00:10:19.640
I've seen him conduct a few times.

00:10:19.780 --> 00:10:20.240
Then...

00:10:20.470 --> 00:10:21.930
I'll introduce you to him.

00:10:22.900 --> 00:10:23.360
Really?

00:10:23.540 --> 00:10:23.870
Come.

00:10:30.350 --> 00:10:31.500
What's wrong with you?

00:10:31.500 --> 00:10:33.560
Something came up at your home again?

00:10:43.660 --> 00:10:44.740
Listen,

00:10:45.500 --> 00:10:46.540
if you get hammered later,

00:10:46.540 --> 00:10:47.740
I won't take you home.

00:10:48.260 --> 00:10:49.870
I'll ask Yi Lan to come get you.

00:10:49.870 --> 00:10:50.420
Don't.

00:10:53.260 --> 00:10:54.460
If you ask her to come,

00:10:55.740 --> 00:10:57.470
I'll break off our friendship.

00:10:58.140 --> 00:10:59.470
Seriously?

00:11:08.260 --> 00:11:09.460
You confessed to her?

00:11:12.620 --> 00:11:13.550
How did you know?

00:11:14.230 --> 00:11:15.160
Did she tell you?

00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:18.500
Even a fool can tell you like her.

00:11:31.110 --> 00:11:32.240
So she rejected you?

00:11:44.500 --> 00:11:45.710
I thought

00:11:48.070 --> 00:11:50.330
we'd be together forever no matter what.

00:11:52.260 --> 00:11:53.020
But...

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:56.550
now she's left me.

00:11:59.140 --> 00:12:00.230
Forever?

00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:03.230
Forever.

00:12:04.660 --> 00:12:05.380
Really?

00:12:07.900 --> 00:12:08.260
I...

00:12:08.900 --> 00:12:09.620
Yeah.

00:12:09.870 --> 00:12:12.740
Only you and I
can be together forever, okay?

00:12:12.740 --> 00:12:13.500
Buddy.

00:12:17.260 --> 00:12:18.350
Forever.

00:12:20.260 --> 00:12:21.110
Chen Fan.

00:12:21.350 --> 00:12:22.140
President Chen.

00:12:22.140 --> 00:12:23.230
Mr. Chen.

00:12:25.420 --> 00:12:26.540
For those words,

00:12:27.370 --> 00:12:29.800
I must drink a toast to you.

00:12:35.230 --> 00:12:36.020
Okay.

00:12:36.870 --> 00:12:39.730
Today, however much you drink,
I'll drink the same.

00:12:41.780 --> 00:12:42.980
You don't believe me?

00:12:49.870 --> 00:12:51.950
Welcome to the broken hearts club.

00:12:52.100 --> 00:12:53.030
How did you know?

00:12:53.110 --> 00:12:54.040
How did you know?

00:12:54.050 --> 00:12:55.140
Alright, alright.

00:12:55.660 --> 00:12:56.670
Forget it.

00:13:08.590 --> 00:13:09.870
Actually,

00:13:11.620 --> 00:13:12.140
I...

00:13:13.020 --> 00:13:16.290
We have both already very sincerely

00:13:17.500 --> 00:13:19.560
expressed our true feelings, but...

00:13:20.350 --> 00:13:22.110
when it comes to love,

00:13:25.590 --> 00:13:26.930
it really is

00:13:27.870 --> 00:13:29.400
something you can't force.

00:13:41.190 --> 00:13:42.600
So I don't think you...

00:13:45.140 --> 00:13:46.400
should blame Yi Lan...

00:13:46.710 --> 00:13:47.590
too much.

00:14:01.620 --> 00:14:02.660
Maybe,

00:14:04.140 --> 00:14:05.380
perhaps,

00:14:08.110 --> 00:14:09.020
probably,

00:14:10.110 --> 00:14:10.910
you should...

00:14:11.110 --> 00:14:12.260
just let it go.

00:14:24.620 --> 00:14:25.380
After all,

00:14:25.870 --> 00:14:28.200
you've known each other for so many years.

00:14:30.780 --> 00:14:32.380
Continuing to be friends...

00:14:33.350 --> 00:14:34.410
is pretty good too.

00:14:53.740 --> 00:14:54.740
Are you blind?

00:14:57.540 --> 00:14:58.740
Don't. Don't. Don't.

00:15:01.110 --> 00:15:02.080
Screw you!

00:15:03.990 --> 00:15:06.000
This is wonderful!

00:15:08.420 --> 00:15:09.030
You hit me?

00:15:09.380 --> 00:15:10.260
Guys, hit them!

00:15:10.540 --> 00:15:11.400
Surround them!

00:15:20.230 --> 00:15:21.830
What happened to your mouth?

00:15:22.470 --> 00:15:23.270
It's nothing.

00:15:38.020 --> 00:15:38.620
Shan.

00:15:45.500 --> 00:15:46.520
That day,

00:15:46.740 --> 00:15:47.870
I was too impulsive.

00:15:48.140 --> 00:15:48.750
I'm sorry.

00:15:52.870 --> 00:15:53.470
It's okay.

00:15:57.660 --> 00:15:58.020
You...

00:15:58.020 --> 00:15:58.620
So...

00:16:01.990 --> 00:16:02.740
S-So,

00:16:02.740 --> 00:16:04.470
the person... in your heart

00:16:04.470 --> 00:16:06.130
has always been Professor Ye?

00:16:09.740 --> 00:16:10.200
Then...

00:16:10.380 --> 00:16:11.980
Then that day, why did you...

00:16:12.230 --> 00:16:13.290
When I asked you...

00:16:21.620 --> 00:16:22.480
Between you...

00:16:22.620 --> 00:16:23.480
and Lan,

00:16:23.900 --> 00:16:24.830
what's going on?

00:16:27.050 --> 00:16:28.110
I confessed to her.

00:16:30.590 --> 00:16:31.790
You confessed to her?

00:16:32.200 --> 00:16:33.690
Didn't you tell me to confess to her?

00:16:33.690 --> 00:16:33.990
I...

00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:37.060
I didn't tell you to confess
in such a hurry.

00:16:37.380 --> 00:16:39.310
You didn't say that that day, Shan.

00:16:42.410 --> 00:16:44.740
Then let me
have a good talk with you today.

00:16:47.620 --> 00:16:48.470
Do you know

00:16:49.110 --> 00:16:51.370
what the most important thing in love is?

00:16:54.420 --> 00:16:56.550
Distance makes the heart grow fonder.

00:16:58.230 --> 00:16:59.830
You need to learn restraint.

00:17:00.420 --> 00:17:02.310
You need to give her space to...

00:17:02.620 --> 00:17:04.109
to grow and feel.

00:17:06.260 --> 00:17:06.920
Restraint.

00:17:07.660 --> 00:17:08.390
Understand?

00:17:24.780 --> 00:17:26.500
[Do Not Disturb]

00:17:26.660 --> 00:17:29.060
Distance makes the heart grow fonder.

00:17:29.350 --> 00:17:30.950
You need to learn restraint.

00:17:41.550 --> 00:17:42.180
[Student Practice Room 10]

00:17:58.220 --> 00:17:59.550
I have a piece of bad news

00:18:00.460 --> 00:18:01.940
and a piece of worse news.

00:18:03.790 --> 00:18:05.070
Which one do you want to hear first?

00:18:05.070 --> 00:18:05.730
The bad one.

00:18:06.590 --> 00:18:07.030
The bad one?

00:18:07.030 --> 00:18:07.270
Mm.

00:18:09.380 --> 00:18:10.250
Xiaole...

00:18:10.660 --> 00:18:11.620
confessed to me.

00:18:16.260 --> 00:18:16.740
And?

00:18:17.420 --> 00:18:18.820
What about the worse one?

00:18:20.070 --> 00:18:21.490
I confessed to Shan.

00:18:22.620 --> 00:18:25.350
What?

00:18:27.030 --> 00:18:27.940
And the result?

00:18:28.620 --> 00:18:29.740
The result is...

00:18:30.110 --> 00:18:31.310
I rejected him.

00:18:32.110 --> 00:18:32.870
And he...

00:18:33.070 --> 00:18:33.830
rejected me.

00:18:35.010 --> 00:18:37.940
Why did you confess to Shan?

00:18:38.550 --> 00:18:39.910
I don't know either.

00:18:39.970 --> 00:18:41.500
I thought I liked him.

00:18:41.620 --> 00:18:43.280
What made you think like that?

00:18:47.940 --> 00:18:49.040
But it's so weird.

00:18:49.140 --> 00:18:50.580
After Shan rejected me,

00:18:50.660 --> 00:18:51.980
I wasn't sad at all.

00:18:52.380 --> 00:18:53.910
And I looked it up online.

00:18:54.070 --> 00:18:56.220
They say the signs of loving someone

00:18:56.310 --> 00:18:57.640
are... feeling jealous

00:18:57.900 --> 00:18:58.870
and being possessive.

00:18:58.870 --> 00:18:59.350
Mm.

00:18:59.380 --> 00:19:02.230
And taking the initiative
to share your life with them.

00:19:02.230 --> 00:19:02.590
Mm.

00:19:02.590 --> 00:19:04.380
And taking the initiative to apologize.

00:19:04.380 --> 00:19:07.110
I indeed have never acted
like that towards Shan.

00:19:07.830 --> 00:19:08.830
Isn't that...

00:19:08.900 --> 00:19:10.620
how you act towards Xiaole?

00:19:10.790 --> 00:19:11.380
Mm.

00:19:15.460 --> 00:19:16.180
Really?

00:19:18.460 --> 00:19:18.870
Mm.

00:19:24.820 --> 00:19:26.870
What exactly is love?

00:19:34.900 --> 00:19:36.030
I don't know either.

00:19:49.310 --> 00:19:49.830
Look.

00:19:49.930 --> 00:19:50.810
[Hailan University]

00:19:57.220 --> 00:19:59.290
Say yes! Say yes!

00:20:03.380 --> 00:20:04.550
Show the ring.

00:20:04.620 --> 00:20:05.720
Yes.

00:20:06.380 --> 00:20:07.290
Where's yours?

00:20:07.900 --> 00:20:10.420
This video has gone viral
in the group chat.

00:20:11.660 --> 00:20:13.550
They are such a perfect match.

00:20:13.620 --> 00:20:14.150
-Mm.
-Mm.

00:20:14.660 --> 00:20:15.970
Why did they break up?

00:20:17.620 --> 00:20:18.970
I heard from classmates

00:20:19.140 --> 00:20:20.400
it might be because

00:20:20.420 --> 00:20:21.880
Professor Ye went abroad.

00:20:23.620 --> 00:20:24.680
Look at this video.

00:20:24.980 --> 00:20:27.140
Professor Ye was so lively and cheerful.

00:20:27.140 --> 00:20:28.940
So different from how she is now.

00:20:29.980 --> 00:20:31.350
Shan also told me

00:20:31.550 --> 00:20:33.750
there's been someone he can't let go of.

00:20:36.610 --> 00:20:39.270
He still can't forget her
after all these years?

00:20:40.180 --> 00:20:40.920
Do you think

00:20:40.940 --> 00:20:42.510
they've both stayed single

00:20:42.620 --> 00:20:44.880
because they've been waiting
for each other?

00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:46.260
Shan also told me

00:20:46.550 --> 00:20:48.650
his understanding of love is

00:20:48.900 --> 00:20:50.360
long-term companionship

00:20:50.540 --> 00:20:51.800
and growing together.

00:20:52.550 --> 00:20:53.630
Maybe...

00:20:54.140 --> 00:20:56.600
they truly have been waiting
for each other.

00:21:01.940 --> 00:21:03.940
Why think so much when in love?

00:21:04.700 --> 00:21:06.220
That's way too complicated.

00:21:06.220 --> 00:21:06.870
Mm.

00:21:32.380 --> 00:21:34.110
My cello's endpin has arrived.

00:21:34.750 --> 00:21:35.140
Oh.

00:21:37.830 --> 00:21:38.790
Let me take a look for you.

00:21:38.790 --> 00:21:39.590
Wait a second.

00:21:56.270 --> 00:21:58.940
You're still using this cello
after all these years?

00:21:58.940 --> 00:22:00.200
The endpin is worn out.

00:22:00.790 --> 00:22:01.650
I have new ones.

00:22:01.830 --> 00:22:02.760
Want to see them?

00:22:03.620 --> 00:22:05.880
I've grown attached to it over the years.

00:22:08.940 --> 00:22:09.940
Can you fix it?

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:11.990
Not sure.

00:22:12.310 --> 00:22:13.590
It depends on whether the cello

00:22:13.590 --> 00:22:14.850
is willing to be fixed.

00:22:17.830 --> 00:22:19.690
You said before you lacked parts,

00:22:20.140 --> 00:22:21.340
so I've been waiting.

00:22:22.460 --> 00:22:22.940
What?

00:22:23.980 --> 00:22:25.980
You went to fix the cello stealthily?

00:22:25.980 --> 00:22:27.470
Who was being stealthy?

00:22:27.900 --> 00:22:30.100
The parts arrived, so I just went there.

00:22:30.420 --> 00:22:31.310
I saw you were in class,

00:22:31.310 --> 00:22:33.040
so I didn't want to disturb you.

00:22:33.220 --> 00:22:34.420
Stealthy?

00:22:34.890 --> 00:22:37.740
Did you go specifically on that day?

00:22:39.350 --> 00:22:40.550
It was a coincidence.

00:22:41.110 --> 00:22:42.110
A coincidence?

00:22:48.940 --> 00:22:50.900
This is the first record I gave you.

00:22:51.380 --> 00:22:52.980
You've kept it all this time?

00:22:57.870 --> 00:22:59.330
Of course I should keep it.

00:22:59.380 --> 00:23:01.710
That record is pretty precious after all.

00:23:03.660 --> 00:23:07.190
It's not like I have to throw it away
just because it was from you.

00:23:08.700 --> 00:23:09.140
Well,

00:23:09.620 --> 00:23:13.220
can you stop touching other people's stuff
without permission?

00:23:17.220 --> 00:23:19.080
I'll leave the cello here for now.

00:23:19.380 --> 00:23:20.980
I'll come get it another day.

00:23:23.700 --> 00:23:24.940
Fix it well for me.

00:23:26.900 --> 00:23:28.760
I'll let you know when it's fixed.

00:24:07.870 --> 00:24:08.510
Xiaole!

00:24:09.940 --> 00:24:11.070
What happened to your face?

00:24:11.070 --> 00:24:12.670
My wisdom tooth is inflamed.

00:24:14.090 --> 00:24:16.770
The light and shadow in my photos
haven't been great.

00:24:16.770 --> 00:24:17.900
Can you take a look for me?

00:24:17.900 --> 00:24:18.380
Sure.

00:24:31.150 --> 00:24:32.210
[Characteristics of DSLR Cameras]

00:24:32.230 --> 00:24:33.460
[Accurately Master
the Shooting Environment]

00:24:33.480 --> 00:24:34.730
[Faster Focusing Speed]

00:24:37.980 --> 00:24:38.510
Yi Lan,

00:24:38.830 --> 00:24:42.140
are you close with Tong Xiaole
from the Department of Photography?

00:24:42.140 --> 00:24:43.850
Are you his girlfriend?

00:24:44.410 --> 00:24:45.660
I'm his childhood friend.

00:24:45.660 --> 00:24:46.220
Why?

00:24:46.220 --> 00:24:46.900
I see.

00:24:47.350 --> 00:24:48.880
Then we all misunderstood.

00:24:49.590 --> 00:24:50.870
I'm a sophomore.

00:24:51.140 --> 00:24:53.270
Could you please help give this to him?

00:25:39.870 --> 00:25:47.140
[I like you]

00:26:22.660 --> 00:26:23.620
Xiaole.

00:26:24.870 --> 00:26:26.080
I'm sorry.

00:26:27.540 --> 00:26:29.640
Actually, I seriously thought

00:26:30.880 --> 00:26:32.490
about what you said that day.

00:26:33.460 --> 00:26:34.790
It was too sudden.

00:26:35.700 --> 00:26:36.690
I think...

00:26:37.900 --> 00:26:38.960
going from friends

00:26:39.140 --> 00:26:40.000
to lovers

00:26:41.590 --> 00:26:43.310
is a huge leap.

00:26:44.180 --> 00:26:44.660
I...

00:26:48.970 --> 00:26:50.890
I hope we can still be friends.

00:26:52.350 --> 00:26:52.980
Is that okay?